diff:1372686014:1372654333:=44,45c44,47%0a%3c %0a%3c %0a---%0a> * Members of the Lucifuge cannot have been in San Diego from 1997-2002. The can be natives of San Diego, but a reason for being "out of town" for that period must be included in the backstory, whether it be personal or some assignment.\\%0a> * Members of Aegis Kai Doru undergo the First Initiation at a labyrinth in Sacramento, if they are/were recruited in the San Diego area. Members from elsewhere would have undergone the First Initiation wherever is geographically appropriate.\\%0a> * Territories that the "Your Friends and Neighbors" Endowment applies to will be formalized when the first dot of that Endowment is taken, at character creation or otherwise. Bear in mind that having influence/friends/etc. in a territory does not imply total control of that territory.%0a> %0a70a73,78%0a> Cell Membership - +3 XP\\%0a> Compact Status - +2 XP\\%0a> Character tied in to Setting Theme - +2 XP\\%0a> Occult 1 or less - +1 XP%0a> %0a> Cells can use their +3s to purchase one cell appropriate tactic at creation.%0a
